body: Hi, I am trying to run a simulation definition downloaded from Hydra , Natural ventilation simulation and my E+ component is giving me this message. I had some issues before and managed to solve them, however this time I'm at a loss. Thanks for your help [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/9Dz4T2phCGF7Z5djuEEvPQZa0t2MgZiyWq08UCqQRkfIPGuUBmBp-iQdgdtpo*oK1t4Y0wXiVwKTWi-f1pWBFb4MsXpe7ylP/EProblem.JPG)

replies.body:
Hi Phil,[
](http://www.grasshopper3d.com/profile/PhilVelectric) You need to update LB and HB component of this file. After the updating, some of the components in the development sometimes they change the amount of input/output items. For this case you need to replace/reinserting these components. -Omid

Hi Omid,

Thanks for responding,

I had tried that but I still get the same error, I may have a bad installation this error appears with all the sample files I test.

I'll try a reinstall and see if the problem remains.

Have a good day.

Phil
